Our Mission...At Greene Lyon Group, our mission is to develop new technologies for recycling precious metals that are cheaper, faster, and more sustainable than the conventional methods they replace.




Our technologies will make it economically compelling to recycle precious metals in an environmentally responsible manner and thereby help mitigate the negative environmental consequences of global growth. We will create value for our shareholders, build a legacy we can be proud of, and have fun.




Our Vision...Greene Lyon Group will be a premier provider of sustainable precious metal recycling technologies for a wide range of materials across multiple industries and will be a leader in the global transition to a circular economy and sustainable materials management.


